itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway are joined by AJ Buckley, star of CBS’s ‘SEAL Team’, while he is on the way to get a COVID test. They talk shooting action scenes during COVID, Andrew Cuomo’s nipple studs, Gavin Newsome ruining California with a smile, how their kids have regressed because of COVID school restrictions, and Alicia Silverstone baby bird feeding her toddler. Plus AJ chats about his diaper bag company Paperclip — Papercliplife.com.
